snippet.title: Gurei - Official Gameplay Trailer | Latin American Games Showcase
snippet.description: Get a fresh look at the world, gameplay, and combat of Gurei in this latest trailer for the upcoming action platformer game. In Gurei, face challenging enemies inspired by Japanese mythology and acquire their powers. Choose your fights in any order, knowing that each opponent gets stronger as the game progresses. Gurei will be available on PC.
